Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.15,0:22:59.44,cned,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在某處呼喚我
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.62,0:23:04.99,cned,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,溫柔的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.18,0:23:08.71,cned,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從遠方傳來
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.88,0:23:11.28,cned,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心為之而動
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.49,0:23:14.65,cned,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請告訴我
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.84,0:23:22.22,cned,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這悲傷的預感將是否成真
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.71,0:23:28.13,cned,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,未曾知曉的心願
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.31,0:23:35.33,cned,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,漸漸浮現
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.55,0:23:41.55,cned,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直有個夢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.73,0:23:47.49,cned,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夢中迷惘 而充滿自由
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.70,0:23:53.14,cned,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,輕聲許下願望
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.35,0:23:58.55,cned,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好想和大家一起
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.53,0:24:06.22,cned,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相視而笑
